    overview:
      'Filing an insurance claim is a process most cannabis business owners hope to avoid but must be prepared for. When a loss occurs, whether from theft, fire, product liability, equipment failure, or employee injury, knowing how to document the event, notify your insurer, and navigate the claims process can mean the difference between a full recovery and a financially devastating outcome. This guide covers the claims process for every major coverage type in cannabis insurance.',
